        </linklist>
        <comment>Dual specificity protein phosphatase 6 [1].
DUSP6 inactivates MAP kinases and has a specificity for the ERK family. MEK1/2 inhibitor U0126 treatment significantly reduces the expression of wellknown targets of ERK (FOS, MYC, DUSP6) [2].
</comment>
      </annotation>
